Yes, this isn't a bug, this is an intentional change of the implementation of [DocumentSerializer.to_internal_value()](https://github.com/umutbozkurt/django-rest-framework-mongoengine/blob/master/rest_framework_mongoengine/serializers.py#L187) to keep validated_data an OrderedDict and not clutter it with EmbeddedDocuments. Now each EmbeddedDocumentSerializer also receives _validated_data attribute with sub-json and walks through it. Sorry that it breaks your code.

